@startuml
hide footbox

title Request Tracking Modes

== Simple (tracking-mode=simple) ==

Client -> Gateway : POST /api/data
Gateway --> Client : 202 {traceId, _links: {status}}

Client -> Gateway : GET /status/{traceId}
Gateway --> Client : {status: "ACCEPTED"}

note over Gateway : downstream processing
Client -> Gateway : GET /status/{traceId}
Gateway --> Client : {status: "PROCESSED"}

== Attachments (tracking-mode=attachments) ==

Client -> Gateway : POST /api/upload
Gateway --> Client : 202 {traceId, _links: {status, attachments}}

note over Gateway : status = COLLECTING_ATTACHMENTS

Client -> Gateway : POST /attachments/{traceId}
Gateway --> Client : 202 (attachment accepted)
note over Gateway : Notify signals Wait

Client -> Gateway : POST /attachments/{traceId}
Gateway --> Client : 202 (attachment accepted)
note over Gateway : Wait releases parent\nstatus = PROCESSING

Client -> Gateway : POST /attachments/{traceId}
Gateway --> Client : 409 (window closed)

@enduml
